{"tid":379127,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[感性問題]一人分享一樣自己嘅comfort food","createTime":"2017-08-29T04:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T02:26:42.000Z","uid":81413,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90e3f4f19ff5ed6ea4bb8ca2dc77b5dc6e8d410d","tid":379127,"uid":81413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:49:45.000Z","msg":"我嘅comfort food係老母整嘅大雜燴湯通粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每次聽到老母話『烚通粉食』就會好開心，明明食過無數次都仲係好期待。<br />\n通常係史雲生雞湯溝少少水做湯底，有切碎嘅菜心、牛肉片、番茄，同埋粟米粒，用傳統彎形通粉，用料簡單但效果好好。<br />\n<br />\nComfort food 特點就係，做法/用料簡單，但有種難以言喻嘅魔力。好似老母每次捧出黎嘅嗰煲通粉，打開蓋嗰下好似瞬間將你催眠，然後一言不發咁，兩隻手就會自動自覺攞起湯羹同碗機械式咁『畢』啲粉落碗度，然後再機械式咁一啖一啖放入口。情況有啲似開片打J嗰陣，左青龍位置點set，右滑鼠要禁邊啲icon，全部已經intuitive，一絲遲疑都無。<br />\n<br />\n成件事好似個邪教儀式咁，你根本停唔倒。碗粉湯底清清地唔係啲咩深刻濃味，粉同菜肉比例奇奇怪怪，裝到個碗瀉咁濟；但正正係咁食完一碗又一碗，添完又添，連湯都飲曬。直至食到極限，見到碗底，先驚覺儀式已經完成，又一次係自己comfort zone裡面忘我暢遊，樂不思蜀。<br />\n<br />\ncomfort food嗰種comfort，係要最唔comfortable嘅時候先會真正察覺，例如，而家喺外國自己孤身一人。唔係話無材料，亦都唔係話唔識整，只係，一煲獨食大雜燴通粉，整咗出黎，又如何？<br />\n<br />\n屌，too long添，anyway磚已拋"},{"pid":"8cf5568551c12466837f0821e9952997f70e8dd8","tid":379127,"uid":127611,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"樓主老母整嘅大雜燴湯通粉"},{"pid":"663d2416fab538b81296e50a0ced27a015009b35","tid":379127,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:27:12.000Z","msg":"老母整嘅炆雞翼 不解釋因為係老母煮嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d606043be72b7882e2096eea688e69cc268c392","tid":379127,"uid":30377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:33:22.000Z","msg":"老母包既壽司<br />\n成本仲低過平時一餐飯 剩係用柴菜同飯包腸仔同平蛋柳<br />\n但我已經可以食一大碟 幾歲食到呢家仲係好鐘意 講起又想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68887987c15500756538c3fa98e690a5df6cbca9","tid":379127,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老母包既壽司<br />\n成本仲低過平時一餐飯 剩係用柴菜同飯包腸仔同平蛋柳<br />\n但我已經可以食一大碟 幾歲食到呢家仲係好鐘意 講起又想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係, 就算屋企冇日本豉油, 用生抽都一樣好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700e0b193c1170569e1e77693ea6fc71e9a6e642","tid":379127,"uid":91895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次收工只要食到燒賣都會即刻覺得唔累<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35eba02b6a079d189599d64dcf4dd6ed9bedb2a2","tid":379127,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:28:34.000Z","msg":"M記任何食物"},{"pid":"b7e01ff912dd49a05f5698b0946ce787a81a8d68","tid":379127,"uid":54597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M記任何食物</blockquote><br />\nX2"},{"pid":"55fa36feb3c22839e114518f073004e1632d1af7","tid":379127,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"老母整既大雜燴烏冬 唔要湯 落芝麻醬"},{"pid":"6685e71bd172d8d89a0d73117239e5f2abf40129","tid":379127,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"屋企人整嘅<br />\n蕃茄薯仔湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、<br />\n雪菜火鴨絲烏冬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6c8aa577c6c5e1f711dc4c838bbb720a7e8144","tid":379127,"uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"xanax"},{"pid":"05598f285cf833299e000672a3ef7aba637c5c5f","tid":379127,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:41:36.000Z","msg":"自己煮既所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7c3c584e59c7aa1d6f8c82f1be3fb82c741857","tid":379127,"uid":77092,